Candwriter LLC is the company that produced BitLife and a number of other apps available on the [https://play.google.com/store/apps/dev?id=8094408836964062012&hl=en_US&gl=US Google Play Store] and [https://apps.apple.com/us/developer/candywriter-llc/id284954685 App Store.] They usually produce apps for iOS, as BitLife was first intended to be, but have made some games for Android and are now working on updating the Android version of BitLife (albeit a bit slowly).

